s:1070:"<div class="no-overflow"><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">Topics for speaking in the POD: </p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">1) What have been my top 2-3 insights from the session and/or the practices during the week? </p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">                                                                            OR</p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;"> 2) When I practice self awareness by observing  'WHAT' I do instead of 'WHY' I do, my insights were…<br /></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">ACTIVITY GUIDELINE:</p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">Each person can take 3 minutes to speak without interruption in the POD. Once all participants have had their time, there can be a free flowing discussion in the POD.<br /></p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">SPECIAL INSTRUCTIONS:</p><p dir="ltr" style="text-align:left;">When a person is speaking, the other practice mindful listening - not interrupting AND giving the speaker their complete attention.<br /></p></div>";